<ab facs="#facs_16_r1l12">tun <expan>ſull<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd <expan>getraw<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> wol . Jr helft den <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> alſo </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_16_r1l13">eins <expan>vnu<ex>er</ex>dıngt<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>recht<ex>en</ex></expan> das <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır mıt <expan>wıll<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> vmb eẅch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_16_r1l14"><expan>v<ex>er</ex>dıenen</expan> vnd lat vns <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> eẅr <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> <expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> <expan>wıd<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>wıſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_16_r1l15">bey <expan>dıſ<ex>em</ex></expan> <expan>bott<ex>en</ex></expan> ob Jr / den <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> eıns <expan>vnu<ex>er</ex>dıngt<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>recht<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>helff<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_16_r1l16">vnd des alſo tag ſecʒen wellet daʒ wır vns darnach <expan>wıſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_16_r1l18">ʒe <expan>rıcht<ex>en</ex></expan> . </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_16_r1l17"><expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> dıe <expan>Pet<ex>ri</ex></expan> et Paulȷ <expan>App<ex>oſto</ex>lo<ex>rum</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_15" id="7v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Heymran Nothaft zu <expan>Wermb<ex>er</ex>g</expan>,
                            <expan>pfleg<ex>er</ex></expan> zu dem Barkstein </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Heymran, als ir uns
                            <expan>jecz<ex>unden</ex></expan>
<expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von des
                            <expan>gefang<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> zu der Weyden und den
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>ein<ex>en</ex></expan> tag geseczt auf den <app>
<note><q type="date"><expan>nehst<ex>en</ex></expan>
                                eritag</q>03.07.1414</note>
</app> doch in <expan>sölich<ex>er</ex></expan> beschaiden, wenn der
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> recht vollfürt
                            <expan>w<ex>er</ex>de</expan>, so <expan>sull<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir
                        ewch von sölichs <expan>v<ex>er</ex>greiffens</expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>, daz die <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> getan
                                <expan>sull<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, als ir maint,
                            <expan>wid<ex>er</ex>umb</expan>
<expan>dess<ex>elben</ex></expan> tags eins <expan>recht<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        sein vor den von <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> Weyden, doch mit <pb facs="#facs_16" id="8r"/><expan>sölich<ex>er</ex></expan> beschaiden, daz ewch
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> recht an dem
                            <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>keine<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>schad<ex>en</ex></expan> bring, <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> daz
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> recht vor gank habe, das
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir wol
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nom<ex>en</ex></expan>, also
                                <expan>bitt<ex>en</ex></expan> wir aber ewr
                                <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>fleiszikl<ex>ich</ex></expan>, daz ir den
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> zu <expan>demselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gefang<ex>en,</ex></expan> der der <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>recht<ex>er</ex></expan> geschol ist, ein slewnig
                                <expan>unv<ex>er</ex>dingt</expan> recht laszet geen und
                            <add>auch</add> des <expan>ein<ex>en</ex></expan> rechttag seczt, den
                        die <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>erlang<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>mug<ex>en</ex></expan>. Und wenn den <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
                        zu dem <expan>gefang<ex>en</ex></expan> ein
                            <expan>unv<ex>er</ex>dingt</expan> recht also
                            <expan>gang<ex>en</ex></expan> ist und gericht wirt, bedürft ir denn
                        eins <expan>recht<ex>en</ex></expan> von uns von des
                                <expan>vorges<ex>chriben</ex></expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>greiffens</expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en,</ex></expan> daz die <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> getan
                                <expan>sull<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, als ir maint, des wir doch pillich
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>trag<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>w<ex>er</ex>en,</expan> als uns dunkt, so
                            <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir ewch eins
                            <expan>frewntl<ex>ich</ex></expan>
<expan>recht<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> sein an den <expan>stett<ex>en</ex></expan>,
                        da wir das pillich tun <expan>sull<ex>e</ex>n.</expan> Und
                                <expan>getraw<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> wol, ir helft den
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> also eins
                                <expan>unv<ex>er</ex>dingt<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>recht<ex>en</ex></expan>, das <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir mit
                                <expan>will<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> umb ewch <expan>v<ex>er</ex>dienen.</expan> Und
                        lat uns <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> ewr
                            <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan>
<expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>
<expan>wid<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan> bey <expan>dis<ex>em</ex></expan>
<expan>bott<ex>en</ex></expan>, ob ir den <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
                        eins <expan>unv<ex>er</ex>dingt<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>recht<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>helff<ex>en</ex></expan> und des also tag seczen wellet, daz wir uns
                        darnach <expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan> ze <expan>richt<ex>en</ex></expan>.
                                <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> die <expan>Pet<ex>ri</ex></expan> et
                        Pauli <expan>app<ex>osto</ex>lo<ex>rum</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
